snippet.title: Nick Johnson
snippet.description:
You get the straight truth about cities and states across the US. This is kind of a socio-geographical-political perspective on what's wrong and right about the United States. I also consult on where you should move. Email me!

Venmo me if you love it so much: @Nick-Johnson-276. 

Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/NickJohnsonYouTube?fan_landing=true

You can buy my songs on iTunes: https://music.apple.com/us/album/a-song-about-montana-single/1522375353

Mappy stuff: Tee shirts and Mugs, people! https://my-store-578844.creator-spring.com/

Email me at robikmarketing1@gmail.com

Send my manager, Sage an email to: NickJohnsonNC18@gmail.com

Most of the music I use is from the YouTube Audio Library. Examples: 

CGI Snake, Air Hockey Saloon by Chris Zabriskie
Candlepower by Chris Zabriskie
Divider by Chris Zabriskie
It's Always too Late to Start Over by Chris Zabriskie
Perception by BenSound
And stuff by Kevin MacLeod (he's great)
